<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-32-0520 </DOCNO><TEXT>The author discusses the importance of lignite as a source of fuel inthe EEC area, but adds that special precautions are needed when employingpulverised lignite. Describes the characteristics of this fuel as a backgroundto explaining the vital safety measures which have to be taken such asinternal and external precautions and checks (leaks, earth connections,implosion valve, explosion valves). Finally presents an installationplan featuring data-processor control. 3 tabs., 7 figs., 7 refs.</TEXT></DOC>